WHAT WE COLLECT FROM YOU?
We are collecting the following personal information from you:
Preferences and data about your use of our services
Device information like android id, device model and Advertise Id
At the time of Registration, Collecting Internet Protocol Address for serving data
MAIN FUNCTIONS
We are not collecting or storing any personal data in background process without user known. App is related to camera scanner. App using camera functionality to capture photo for document and adjust automatically as per requirement. Save and share document functionality available in application.
SECURITY
- The security of your personal information is important to us. When you enter sensitive information, we are passing information with https server and also passing security encrypted token to validate request. No method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure, however. Therefore, we cannot guarantee its absolute security. If you have any questions about security on our Web site, you can contact us at
solidappspace@gmail.com
