Permissions that we require
- App for Android requires following permissions to perform normally on your device

1. App will use storage permission to select photo from Gallery for setting as background wallpaper. For that we are using android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE and android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.

2. Wi-Fi connection information : We read the status of Wi-Fi connection on your device to notify you about the same and also intimate you to use application at that time so as to save on your data costs
